Author: RubyPrynne
Text: I'm sorry hon, you're looking for comfort. Not sour, depressing facts.  I understand the excruciating pain of stagnant weightloss--despite all your efforts. I'm there too. ‚ù§    You've suffered with this for a long time.  You're not alone, my friend.  We can get through this.

Author: RubyPrynne
Text: You've plateaued, babe.    What's happened is your metabolism has slowed way the fuck down; it is, essentially, your physiological response to malnurishment.
